        "performedDateTime": "2024",
        "note": [
          {
            "text": "Performed as part of cardiovascular risk stratification following diagnosis of hyperlipidaemia. Demonstrated bilateral increased carotid intima-media thickness consistent with early subclinical atherosclerosis. Findings correlated with prior ischemic stroke and prompted ongoing vascular neurology review."
